tables.table_schema:
CREATE TABLE vehicle_performance_metrics (
    vehicle_id INT,
    timestamp TIMESTAMP,
    speed FLOAT,
    fuel_level FLOAT,
    engine_temperature FLOAT,
    engine_rpm INT
);

CREATE TABLE maintenance_history (
    maintenance_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
    vehicle_id INT,
    maintenance_date DATE,
    maintenance_type VARCHAR(50),
    maintenance_description VARCHAR(255)
);
CREATE TABLE vehicles (vehicle_id INT PRIMARY KEY, make VARCHAR(50), model VARCHAR(50), year INT, mileage INT, last_maintenance_date DATE)
CREATE TABLE performance_metrics (metric_id INT PRIMARY KEY, vehicle_id INT, timestamp TIMESTAMP, speed INT, fuel_consumption DECIMAL, engine_temperature INT)
CREATE TABLE efficiency_metrics (efficiency_id INT PRIMARY KEY, vehicle_id INT, timestamp TIMESTAMP, efficiency_percentage DECIMAL, distance_traveled INT)
CREATE TABLE maintenance_needs (maintenance_id INT PRIMARY KEY, vehicle_id INT, timestamp TIMESTAMP, maintenance_type VARCHAR(50), cost DECIMAL)

CREATE TABLE vehicle_performance_metrics (
    vehicle_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
    metric_timestamp TIMESTAMP,
    speed FLOAT,
    acceleration FLOAT,
    fuel_consumption FLOAT
);

CREATE TABLE maintenance_logs (
    log_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
    vehicle_id INT,
    log_timestamp TIMESTAMP,
    maintenance_type VARCHAR(50),
    maintenance_description TEXT
);
